{"tid":134288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現中國用語大量入侵台灣？ 引起鄉民熱烈討論","createTime":"2017-02-25T11:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T04:43:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a3ec73b7c548faaae01ceaf69cd3583c4d56dd","tid":134288,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>這些詞都來自支那？　支那用語引台灣網友熱議　網友：唔撚係卦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=227508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D227508&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1GMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=2d0efaee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D227508&h=f7b13ccb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=227508</a><br />\n</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n網友在批踢踢上發文，表示「最近中國用語大量入侵台灣，比方說，大媽漸漸取代了大嬸跟阿桑，還有吸引眼球取代了吸引目光，水平也漸漸取代了水準。還有哪些詞，大家還記得被中國取代以前是怎麼說的嗎？有沒有八卦？」<br />\n<br />\n這篇文章一出，引來許多網友討論，想知道到底有哪些日常用語被大陸用語取代，像是「大嬸&rarr;大媽」、「價值觀&rarr;三觀」、「長相&rarr;顏質」、「八年級&rarr;90後」、「高畫質&rarr;高清」、「水準&rarr;水平」、「吸引目光&rarr;吸引眼球。」<br />\n<br />\n除了台灣網友熱烈討論，也有大陸網友提供不一樣的觀點，指出並不是只有大陸用語傳入台灣，許多大陸網友也會使用「啊不就好棒棒」、「沒在怕的」等台灣常見用語。<br />\n<br />\n▼有大陸網友指出，台灣常用的用語也在大陸流行。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2017/02/22/818752-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F818752-XXL.jpg&h=73df899a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"828606c5094ee83c0049d89654fb2c212b95346e","tid":134288,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PTT：[新聞] 中國用語大量入侵台灣？ 鄉民熱烈討論這<br />\n<a href=\"https://pttweb.tw/thread/m-1487733673-a-099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpttweb.tw%2Fthread%2Fm-1487733673-a-099&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1GMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0bccca43\" target=\"_blank\">https://pttweb.tw/thread/m-1487733673-a-099</a></strong></div></span>"},{"pid":"4c937b6c2fc92255137e0e5e7f640219190e6aa4","tid":134288,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"邊係中國用語，台灣都用<br />\n書面語嚟<br />\n97前都有啦<br />\n台仔中文差，自己未見過就話中國用語"},{"pid":"c59c770c68e28c54fec61313486f3416be4688c5","tid":134288,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"淨係6666就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af3c3c18b842a4e83b5aa29a87f72310b1014bf","tid":134288,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83a0c2024e694e20d7cc39958d70ffa7ce45212e","tid":134288,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:11:14.000Z","msg":"流落荒島<br />\n台灣人同中國人溝通完全冇問題<br />\n香港人就完全雞同鴨講"},{"pid":"65daf93b2981209b0cec47b280d767d5a09056b5","tid":134288,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"不用分得那麼細，大家都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f87aa2d722ab64922a5218ee8e20273ba245ae","tid":134288,"uid":3295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊係中國用語，台灣都用<br />\n書面語嚟<br />\n97前都有啦<br />\n台仔中文差，自己未見過就話中國用語</blockquote><br />\n就算都係書面語，都有分中國用語同台灣用語<br />\n就好似都係白話，廣東人用字同香港人用字都唔同<br />\n中國用語入侵係事實"},{"pid":"936b2b5d141f35bb20db06360ccd15a8bdbfcd68","tid":134288,"uid":32007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家都係中國人有咩所謂</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983a2cf9c52d3764ee131ac19cf421afcd35f203","tid":134288,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislik